conference.title: Laracon EU 2019 Madrid
conference.summary: We re bringing Laracon EU to Madrid on May 23rd for a new one-day event. Join speakers Adam Wathan, Matt Stauffer, and many more for a brain-crunching day of talks and community celebration.
